-- Dubai Islamic Bank says to buy 25 pct in Indonesia's Bank Panin Syariah
-- By David French
-- Mon May 19, 2014 06:25AM EDT
-- None



DUBAI, May 19 (Reuters) - Dubai Islamic Bank <DISB.DU> is to purchase a 25 percent stake in Indonesian Islamic lender Bank Panin Syariah <PNBS.JK>, it said in a statement on Monday, adding it could ultimately increase the holding up to 40 percent.

No purchase price was given in the statement, which said the transaction was still subject to regulatory approval.